  function refreshAfterPopup(){try{if(typeof refreshDataSync==='function')refreshDataSync()}catch(_){}try{if(typeof refreshImports==='function')refreshImports()}catch(_){}try{if(typeof renderLocalDataRows==='function')renderLocalDataRows()}catch(_){}try{if(typeof drawImportedObjects==='function')drawImportedObjects()}catch(_){} }
  async function handlePopupAction(btn){const action=btn.getAttribute('data-v322-popup-action')||btn.getAttribute('data-v321-popup-action')||btn.getAttribute('data-v320-popup-action');if(!action)return;const details=btn.closest('details.popup-edit');if(action==='cancel'){try{details&&details.removeAttribute('open')}catch(_){};return}const form=details||btn.closest('.tak-v322-popup,.tak-v321-popup,.tak-v320-popup')||d;parseLatLon(form);const key=btn.getAttribute('data-popup-key')||'',source=btn.getAttribute('data-popup-source')||'object',lid=btn.getAttribute('data-local-id')||'';if(action==='delete'){if(!confirm('Delete this item?'))return;if(lid){await postJson('/api/tak-map/local-data-delete',{ids:[lid]})}else{await postJson('/api/tak-map/popup-edit',{key:key,source:source,delete_item:true})}closePopupFrom(btn);refreshAfterPopup();return}if(action==='save'){const payload={key:key,source:source,name:(form.querySelector('[name="name"]')||{}).value||'',notes:(form.querySelector('[name="notes"]')||{}).value||'',lat:(form.querySelector('[name="lat"]')||{}).value||'',lon:(form.querySelector('[name="lon"]')||{}).value||''};await postJson('/api/tak-map/popup-edit',payload);closePopupFrom(btn);refreshAfterPopup();return}}
  function installHandlers(){if(window.__v322PopupHandlers)return;window.__v322PopupHandlers=true;d.addEventListener('click',function(ev){const close=ev.target&&ev.target.closest&&ev.target.closest('.leaflet-popup.tak-v322-object-popup .leaflet-popup-close-button,.leaflet-popup.tak-v321-object-popup .leaflet-popup-close-button,.leaflet-popup .leaflet-popup-close-button');if(close&&close.closest('.leaflet-popup')){ev.preventDefault();ev.stopPropagation();try{ev.stopImmediatePropagation()}catch(_){};closePopupFrom(close);return false}const btn=ev.target&&ev.target.closest&&ev.target.closest('[data-v322-popup-action],[data-v321-popup-action],[data-v320-popup-action]');if(!btn)return;ev.preventDefault();ev.stopPropagation();try{ev.stopImmediatePropagation()}catch(_){};handlePopupAction(btn).catch(function(e){alert('Popup update failed: '+(e&&e.message||e))});return false},true);const m=getMap();if(m&&m.on&&!window.__v322MapPopupOpenBound){window.__v322MapPopupOpenBound=true;try{m.on('popupopen',function(ev){setTimeout(function(){markPopup(ev&&ev.popup)},0)})}catch(_){}}}
  function installOverrides(){expose('popupEditForm',editForm);expose('pointPopupHtml',pointPopupHtmlV322);expose('layerPopupForObject',layerPopupForObjectV322);expose('featurePopupHtml',featurePopupHtmlV322)}
  function installFetchHook(){try{if(window.__takV322FetchHook)return;const old=window.fetch;if(typeof old!=='function')return;window.fetch=function(input,init){const url=String((typeof input==='string'?input:(input&&input.url))||'');const method=String((init&&init.method)||'GET').toUpperCase();return old.apply(this,arguments).then(function(resp){try{if(method==='POST'&&/\/api\/tak-map\/(import|local-data-delete|import-clear)(\b|\?)/.test(url)){resp.clone().json().then(function(j){if(j&&Array.isArray(j.imports))applyImports(j.imports)}).catch(function(){})}}catch(_){}return resp})};window.__takV322FetchHook=true}catch(_){}}
